    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged; however, the three QoIs all pass quantitative acceptance criteria with E/uval well below 1.96, and the ASTM F1717 protocol is the regulatory standard for this device class. The overall evidence package is judged sufficient to support the submission claim.",
